            "text": "<p><strong>Serves 10–15Includes Chips, Guacamole, 2 Salsas, Rice & Beans.*</strong></p><p><strong>1. CALLE TACO, BURRITOS — $275</strong><br/>• 15 La Calle Tacos<br/>Chicken or Carnitas (or a combination)<br/>• 4 Original Burritos (cut in half)<br/>Choose: Chicken or Carnitas<br/>• Chelas Salad — medium bowl (no meat)</p><p><strong>•</strong></p><p><strong>2. ENCHILADA PACK — $275</strong><br/>• 25 Enchiladas Verdes<br/>Choose: Cheese, Chicken or Carnitas<br/>• Garnishes: Lettuce (medium bowl), Sour Cream, Queso Fresco, Pico de Gallo (½ pint)</p><p><strong>•</strong></p><p><strong>3. CRISPY TACO, BURRITO & QUESADILLA — $275</strong><br/>• 10 Crispy Tacos<br/>Chicken or Carnitas (or a combination)<br/>• 4 Chelas Burritos (cut in half)<br/>Choose: Chicken or Carnitas<br/>• 2 Cheese Quesadilla Trays<br/>(2 cut into 12 pieces)</p><p><strong>•</strong></p><p><strong>4. FAJITAS</strong><br/>• Chicken, Steak or Mixed — $300<br/>• Shrimp — $330<br/>• Garnishes: Guacamole & Limes<br/>• “No’s” – No Onion, Cilantro or Pico de Gallo<br/>*Does not include chips & salsa</p><p><strong>•</strong></p><p><strong>5. BREAKFAST PACK — $250</strong><br/>• 15 Breakfast Tacos<br/>Choose: Mexican chorizo egg or Americano egg bacon tacos<br/>• 4 Breakfast Burritos (cut in half)<br/>Choose: MVP or Chorizo burritos<br/>• Grilled bell peppers and onions (half tray)<br/>• Refried or Black Beans (half tray)<br/></p><p><strong>•</strong></p><p><strong>6. LITTLE BURROS</strong><br/>20 mini burritos<br/>• Bean & Cheese — $70<br/>• Add Chicken — + $20<br/>*Does not include chips & salsa, guac, rice or beans</p><p><strong>•</strong></p><p><strong>EXTRAS</strong><br/>You can purchase any of our meats, rice, beans, salsas, specialty sauces by the pint.<br/>Chips, Salads by large bowls.<br/>Tortillas by the dozen.<br/>Ask for specialty orders that cater to your needs.</p><p>•</p><p></p>"
